Program: The Documentary
Title: Assisted Reproduction
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csxlmm
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 24 Sep 2018
How humans make babies could be about to change, thanks to advances in IVF and reproductive technology. Krupa Padhy meets the new kinds of families that could become the norm, and explores how reproductive technology may soon alter the way all of us make babies. Image: Illustration of sperm approaching an egg (Credit: Science Photo Library) Show less